'''六氟化鈾'''（{{lang-en|uranium hexafluoride}}）是一种[[铀|铀]]的[[化合物|化合物]]，其[[化学式|化学式]]为{{化學式|U|F|6}}。六氟化铀被用于制取[[浓缩铀|浓缩铀]]，因此在[[核工业|核工业]]中有很重要的价值。[[标准状况|标准状况]]下，六氟化铀为灰色的[[晶体|晶体]]。六氟化铀有很强的[[毒性|毒性]]，可与[[水|水]]剧烈反应，并且能腐蚀大多数[[金属|金属]]。它與[[鋁|鋁]]反應溫和，在鋁的表面形成致密的[[氟化铝|氟化铝]]薄膜，阻止反應進一步進行。

== 制取 ==
磨碎鈾礦（[[八氧化三铀|U<sub>3</sub>O<sub>8</sub>]]，或稱“[[黃餅|黃餅]]”），并将其溶于[[硝酸|硝酸]]，產生[[硝酸鈾酰|硝酸鈾酰]]UO<sub>2</sub>(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>溶液。[[萃取|萃取]]纯化后，使硝酸铀酰与[[氨|氨]]反应，生成[[重铀酸铵|重铀酸铵]](NH<sub>4</sub>)<sub>2</sub>U<sub>2</sub>O<sub>7</sub>。加[[氢|氢]][[还原|还原]]得到[[二氧化铀|二氧化铀]]，再与[[氢氟酸|氢氟酸]]反应生成[[四氟化铀|四氟化铀]]。四氟化铀與[[氟|氟]]进行氧化反應產生UF<sub>6</sub>。

== 核燃料循環中的應用 ==
<!-- please explain why its triple point makes it useful in these methods. -->各种主要的铀浓缩方法都需要用到六氟化铀，不论是[[气体扩散法|气体扩散法]]，还是[[气体离心法|气体离心法]]。这是由于六氟化铀的[[三相点|三相点]]为 147 °F （64 °C，337 K），且[[气压|气压]]略高于[[大气压|大气压]]。[[氟|氟]]在自然界只存在一种稳定[[核素|核素]]也是一个原因，因此各种六氟化铀分子的[[相对分子质量|相对分子质量]]差异可以完全归咎于各种铀核素[[相对原子质量|相对原子质量]]的差异。<ref>{{cite web | title = Uranium Enrichment and the Gaseous Diffusion Process | publisher = USEC Inc | url = http://www.usec.com/v2001_02/HTML/Aboutusec_enrichment.asp | accessdate = 2007-09-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071019081831/http://www.usec.com/v2001_02/HTML/Aboutusec_enrichment.asp | archivedate = 2007-10-19 }}</ref>
[[Image:Uranium_hexafluoride_crystals_sealed_in_an_ampoule.jpg|thumb]]
其他所有的氟化鈾將產生固態的[[配位聚合物|配位聚合物]]。

气相扩散法所需用的[[能量|能量]]大约是气体离心法的60倍。尽管如此，其中仅仅有4%的能量被用于制取浓缩铀。

除此之外，[[捷克|捷克]]发展了一种循环使用核燃料的方法：用旧的[[氧化物|氧化物]][[核燃料|核燃料]]与氟气反应生成各种[[氟化物|氟化物]]的混合物，再用[[分馏|分馏]]分离各种组分。

== 储存 ==
目前大约95%的[[贫化铀|贫化铀]]都以六氟化铀的形式被置于气体[[钢瓶|钢瓶]]中，储存在核工厂的附近。每个钢瓶大约含有12.7吨的固体六氟化铀。仅在美国，1993年至2005年期间，就有686,500吨的六氟化铀（57,122瓶）作为贫化铀的储存形式被生产出来。它们被储存在[[俄亥俄州|俄亥俄州]][[朴次茅斯_(俄亥俄州)|樸茨茅斯]]，[[田納西州|田納西州]][[橡树岭_(田纳西州)|橡樹嶺]]和[[肯塔基州|肯塔基州]][[帕迪尤卡_(肯塔基州)|帕迪尤卡]]。<ref>{{cite web | work = Depleted UF<sub>6</sub> FAQs | title = How much depleted uranium hexafluoride is stored in the United States? | url = http://web.ead.anl.gov/uranium/faq/health/faq16.cfm | publisher = [[Argonne_National_Laboratory|Argonne National Laboratory]] }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://web.ead.anl.gov/uranium/documents/index.cfm |title=Documents<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2008-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080216013118/http://web.ead.anl.gov/uranium/documents/index.cfm |archive-date=2008-02-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>六氟化铀很不稳定，与潮湿空气接触时即会反应生成极易溶于水并且毒性很大的 [[铀酰氟|UO<sub>2</sub>F<sub>2</sub>]] 和[[氟化氢|氟化氢]]，因此长期储存六氟化铀会对环境及人的健康造成损害，须定期检查是否有裂缝。<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Institute for Energy and Environmental Research | publication-date = December 1997 | title = What is DUF<sub>6</sub>? Is it dangerous and what should we do with it? | url = http://www.ieer.org/sdafiles/vol_5/5-2/deararj.html | accessdate = 2017-02-23 | language = en | archive-date = 2012-02-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120205184250/http://www.ieer.org/sdafiles/vol_5/5-2/deararj.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

[[File:DUF6_cylinder_leak.gif|255px]]

[[美国|美国]]已经发生过数起涉及六氟化铀的事故。<ref>{{cite web | work = Depleted UF<sub>6</sub> FAQs | title = Have there been accidents involving uranium hexafluoride? | url = http://web.ead.anl.gov/uranium/faq/health/faq30.cfm | publisher = [[Argonne_National_Laboratory|Argonne National Laboratory]] | access-date = 2008-02-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080306020031/http://web.ead.anl.gov/uranium/faq/health/faq30.cfm | archive-date = 2008-03-06 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Uranium Hexafluoride (UF<sub>6</sub>) Tailings: Characteristics, Transport and Storage at the Siberian Chemical Combine (Sibkhimkombinat) Tomsk | format = briefing note | publisher = Large and Associates | date = 5 November 2005 | url = http://www.largeassociates.com/R3139-a1%20frontispiece.pdf | accessdate = 2007-09-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070927034454/http://www.largeassociates.com/R3139-a1%20frontispiece.pdf | archivedate = 2007-09-27 }}</ref>美国政府将 UF<sub>6</sub> 转化为固态的铀[[氧化物|氧化物]]回收。<ref>{{cite web | work = Depleted UF<sub>6</sub> FAQs | title = What is going to happen to the uranium hexafluoride stored in the United States? | url = http://web.ead.anl.gov/uranium/faq/health/faq22.cfm | publisher = [[Argonne_National_Laboratory|Argonne National Laboratory]] }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>但这种回收总共要花费大约1500万到4.5亿[[美元|美元]]。<ref>{{cite web | work = Depleted UF<sub>6</sub> FAQs | title = Are there any currently-operating disposal facilities that can accept all of the depleted uranium oxide that would be generated from conversion of DOE's depleted UF6 inventory? | url = http://web.ead.anl.gov/uranium/faq/health/faq27.cfm | publisher = [[Argonne_National_Laboratory|Argonne National Laboratory]] }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

== 化學性質 ==

固態時的結構由 J.H. Levy、J.C Taylor 和 A.B Waugh所描述。<ref>{{cite journal| author= J.H. Levy, J.C Taylor and A.B Waugh | title=Neutron powder structural studies of UF<sub>6</sub>, MoF<sub>6</sub> and WF<sub>6</sub> at 77 K| journal= Journal of Fluorine Chemistry| year= 1983| pages=29-36| volume=23|doi=10.1016/S0022-1139(00)81276-2 }}</ref>在該論文中，他們利用[[中子衍射|中子衍射]]測定UF<sub>6</sub>、 MoF<sub>6</sub> 和 WF<sub>6</sub> 在77K下的結構。
<center><gallery>
File:Uranium-hexafluoride-crystal-3D-vdW.png|六氟化铀的[[晶体结构|晶体结构]]
</gallery></center>

六氟化铀可作为[[氧化剂|氧化剂]]或[[路易斯酸|路易斯酸]]，易于[[氟离子|氟离子]]结合。如[[氟化铜|氟化铜]]与六氟化铀在[[乙腈|乙腈]]中反应会生成 Cu[UF<sub>7</sub>]<sub>2</sub>.5MeCN。<ref>{{cite journal| author= Berry JA, Poole RT, Prescott A, Sharp DWA, Winfield JM| title= The oxidising and fluoride ion acceptor properties of uranium hexafluoride in acetonitrile| journal= J. Chem. Soc. Dalton Trans.| year= 1976| pages=272|doi=10.1039/DT9760000272}} x</ref>

含有有机[[阳离子|阳离子]]的铀（VI）[[聚合物|聚合物]]已经制得并用[[X光衍射|X光衍射]]分析。<ref>{{cite journal| author= Walker SM, Halasyamani PS, Allen S, O'Hare D| title= From Molecules to Frameworks: Variable Dimensionality in the UO<sub>2</sub>(CH<sub>3</sub>COO)<sub>2</sub>·2H<sub>2</sub>O/HF(aq)/Piperazine System. Syntheses, Structures, and Characterization of Zero-Dimensional (C<sub>4</sub>N<sub>2</sub>H<sub>12</sub>)UO<sub>2</sub>F<sub>4</sub>·3H<sub>2</sub>O, One-Dimensional (C<sub>4</sub>N<sub>2</sub>H<sub>12</sub>)<sub>2</sub>U<sub>2</sub>F<sub>12</sub>·H2</sub>O, Two-Dimensional (C<sub>4</sub>N<sub>2</sub>H<sub>12</sub>)<sub>2</sub>(U<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>F<sub>5</sub>)<sub>4</sub>·11H<sub>2</sub>O, and Three-Dimensional (C<sub>4</sub>N<sub>2</sub>H<sub>12</sub>)U<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>F<sub>6</sub>| journal=[[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]| year= 1999| pages= 10513| volume= 121|doi=10.1021/ja992145f}} x</ref>

